    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Castleridge</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-xl">With Castleridge's immaculate greens and winding walking trails, the community in Castleridge provides abundant open spaces for young couples and growing families with kids, to lead a relaxing life amidst nature. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">With close proximity to recreational venues such as the Don Hartman North East Sportsplex and a variety of shopping malls, residents in Castleridge have a plethora of activities to engage in their leisure hours.</p>
